tora-san 's &lt;unk&gt; ( 男はつらいよ &lt;unk&gt; otoko wa tsurai yo : torajirō &lt;unk&gt; ) aka torasan and the matchmaker ) is a 1984 japanese comedy film directed by yoji yamada . it stars kiyoshi atsumi as torajirō kuruma ( tora-san ) , and kyōko kagawa as his love interest or " madonna " . tora-san 's lovesick is the fourth entry in the popular , long-running otoko wa tsurai yo series .